text: Marisara Pont Marchese (born October 29, 1941) is a Puerto Rican politician. She was the Secretary of State of Puerto Rico for a few months in 2005."Puerto Rico's Gateway to the World", Ediciones Santillana, 2011, , page 195 ==References== Category:Living people Category:Secretaries of state of Puerto Rico Category:1941 births
